Package: ggpatina
Type: Package
Title: Period Aesthetics and Analog Aging Effects for Figures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("John", "Prybylski", , "jprybylski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5802-0539"))
Author: John Prybylski [aut, cre, cph]
Maintainer: John Prybylski <jprybylski@gmail.com>
Description: Provides period-inspired fonts and analog-aging visual effects for figures.
    Includes presets for transparency slides and old journal scans, plus ink bleed,
    Kodachrome-style fade, photocopy misalignment, and a blueprint (cyanotype) style.
